far only be proved for random\nperiodic configurations. Finally, a result on the gap distribution of\nfractional parts of the sequence of square roots of positive integers, which\nextends previous work by Elkies and McMullen, is also obtained.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Aug 2015 08:28:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Feb 2018 12:25:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-06"}
